arts.ttl: Albania vs England predictions: Three Lions to overpower their hosts
arts.sum: England complete a successful World Cup qualifying campaign with a trip to Tirana to face Albania, and Joe Champion expects the Three Lions to turn on the style in Sunday's Group K swansong.

Albania arrive at the final matchday in buoyant spirits after securing a historic play-off place with a game to spare. Sylvinhoâ€™s side are unbeaten in five Group K outings (W3 D2), built not on attack...
